{"_id":"EH2DclhLLq9oyNHq","name":"Leofric's Field of Force","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/defensive/barrier-shield-dome-blue-purple.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>A glittering field of force surrounds a point in space you choose within range. The field can moulded to conform to the edges of a space winthin a radius of 50 feet around the point you cast it on. It can seal gaps in walls, such as doors and windows. The field is infinitely thin but cannot be penetrated by any physical object, creature, or gas. Sound can pass through the field if both sides are filled with air.</p>\n<p>If during the creation of the field it intersects a creature's space, the creature is pushed to a random side of the field. The creature must make a Constitution saving throw against your spell save DC. The creature takes [[/roll 6d8 + @attributes.prof]] lightning damage on a failed save, or half as much on a success.</p>\n<p>The field can only be dispelled by @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.15Fa6q1nH27XfbR8]{Dispel Magic}.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"perm"},"target":{"value":50,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":120,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"material","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"A glittering field springs forth, shining light in all colors of the rainbow","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["6d8 + @attributes.prof","lightning"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":4,"school":"evo","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":true,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"a two inch squared piece of cloth woven from glittering silk","consumed":true,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formu